title: Hour 2 - The New Big Ten
itunes:title: Hour 2 - The New Big Ten
description:
Dan Patrick reacts to the theory that Hall of Fames are being "watered down." Sports Illustrated's Pat Forde joins the show to look at which schools may be the next to change conferences. Plus, Dan gives his thoughts on the big stories surrounding Tom Brady.
